item.title: Error?
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

Lol, how do people manage these errors? Make sure your compiler is searching for the Java files in the right directory - If you’ve moved them to a folder called Java or something, make the appropriate changes to the compiler so it can find the files at their new location.
